ase 6: Testing\n47: \n48: - [ ] **TEST-001**: Write unit tests for JWT signing\n49: - [ ] **TEST-002**: Write unit tests for JWT verification\n50: - [ ] **TEST-003**: Write integration tests\n51: - [ ] **TEST-004**: Write performance benchmarks\n52: \n53: ### Phase 7: Documentation\n54: \n55: - [ ] **DOC-001**: Add godoc comments\n56: - [ ] **DOC-002**: Document configuration options\n57: - [ ] **DOC-003**: Update module README\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ## Acceptance Criteria\n62: \n63: - [ ] JWT tokens can be signed with configurable algorithms\n64: - [ ] JWT tokens can be verified and validated\n65: - [ ] Token expiration is enforced\n66: - [ ] Token refresh mechanism works correctly\n67: - [ ] Authentication middleware integrates with router\n68: - [ ] All unit tests pass with ≥85% coverage\n69: - [ ] Performance benchmarks meet requirements\n70: - [ ] Documentation is complete\n71: \n72: ---\n73: \n74: ## Dependencies\n75: \n76: | Dependency | Source | Usage |\n77: |------------|--------|-------|\n78: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | External | JWT library |\n79: | `pkg/router` (AR-009) | Internal | Router base module |\n80: \n81: ---\n82: \n83: ## Implementation Order\n84: \n85: ```\n86: TASK-001 → TASK-002 → TASK-003 → TASK-010 → TASK-011 → TASK-012\n87:                                               ↓\n88:                               TASK-020 → TASK-021 → TASK-022\n89:                                               ↓\n90:                               TASK-030 → TASK-031 → TASK-032\n91:                                               ↓\n92:                               TASK-040 → TASK-041\n93:                                               ↓\n94:                               TEST-001 → TEST-002 → TEST-003 → TEST-004\n95:                                               ↓\n96:                               DOC-001 → DOC-002 → DOC-003\n97: ```\n\n(End of file - total 97 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Tasks\n\n## Overview\n\