{"type":"text","timestamp":1775851687596,"sessionID":"ses_28704e4cdffeDsBqzmqKixki53","part":{"id":"prt_d79023eba001dx5i91Vo8CRfQh","messageID":"msg_d7901db4a001GAPCbWwdM6TYK1","sessionID":"ses_28704e4cdffeDsBqzmqKixki53","type":"text","text":"Done! I've created a comprehensive `tasks.md` checklist for AR-011 with 11 phases and 80+ atomic tasks covering:\n\n**Key Phases:**\n1. **JWT Types & Claims** - Data structures and configuration\n2. **JWT Authenticator** - Core signing, validation, refresh, revocation\n3. **Token Blacklist** - Memory and Redis-backed revocation\n4. **HTTP Handlers** - Token issuance, refresh, revoke endpoints\n5. **Auth Middleware** - JWT validation middleware with skip paths\n6. **Router Integration** - Apply middleware to routes\n7. **Kubernetes Client** - Service account verification\n8. **Logging & Audit** - Structured audit logging\n9. **Error Handling** - Error types and HTTP mapping\n10. **Testing (TDD)** - 40+ test cases covering unit, integration, and performance\n11. **Documentation** - Godoc and README updates\n\nThe checklist follows the AR-010 pattern with detailed, independently verifiable atomic tasks aligned with the delta-spec requirements.","time":{"start":1775851687594,"end":1775851687594}}}
